-25/39031314_283171130712239_38048015563775330_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bPwNJ-Bqpt0Q7kNvgHhYk-x&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCvtvfG9TT6QfJPxhhoWIyIFyzq_cLSNjN2h9mqNaZShQ&oe=66D2FD27"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "TSVR2560.png", "id": "557783223170073", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031579_557783226503406_7792884008937608733_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=w6j7Tx4KgIAQ7kNvgG31uaJ&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA11UhLQKS3o9I_QydtjEV1Kxjr84Arx7r0tplHuec1zg&oe=66D3075E"}, "display_name": "Trick Shot VR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Have you ever wanted to try doing the craziest trick shots around town? Now you can with Trick Shot VR! Switch between using a ping pong ball, a basketball, or a frisbee to land the best shots. \n\nEach trick shot item has 3 unique levels with their goal item set around the neighborhood. Once all 3 levels are completed in a section, that trick shot item can be used around the neighborhood in Freeplay! \n\nFeatures include :\n- Spawning on Grip - With the spawn on grip feature, you can continue to spawn throwables as many times as you like! \n\n- Interactable Openings - Doors and windows can be opened to add another layer of challenge to shots.\n\n- Moveable Pans - The pots and pans in the kitchen are pickupable. use them to bounce  throws off of!\n\n- Clear Spawned - Too many thrown items? Open the quick hand menu and clear them.\n\n- Dynamic Scoring - Scoring is based off of how far thrown an object is, and how many times it bounced. Each object also has a specific bounce multiplier!\n\nThe real question is, how many bounces can you get, and how far of a throw can you land?  ", "short_description": "Switch between using a ping pong ball, a basketball, or a frisbee to land the craziest trick shots around the neighborhood! How many bounces can you get, and how far can you throw?"}]}, "developer_name": null, "develope